main event: A witness observed an unidentified flying object in Willowick, Ohio on 14 October 1966.
interesting points: The observation was reported to the U.S. Air Force's Project Blue Book., The witness stated that the saucer disappeared from view behind some houses., The witness could not explain the sighting or how they could see the object., The Air Force requested further information from the witness to evaluate the report., The conclusion was that there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: only one witness reported the sighting
